Popular Ex-OAP, Matthew Edafe popularly known as Elegbete1 at Brila Fm 88.9, Lagos anchors a new sport show tagged “SPORTS LOUNGE”. “SPORTS LOUNGE” which comprises of Formula One, Basketball, Football and grassroots football all in one interesting piece is set to take Nigerian sport show to a different level. The Sports Show which is published every Wednesday with the third episode in progress is live on ElegbeteTv YouTube channel as fans troop in to get a full taste of the “delicious meal”. We recalled that, Matthew Edafe and wife welcomed a baby in July, 2019. See Photos: Watch the video below: Source